      "content": "it just feels like a trap. every day i wake up and i see the bills and i see their faces and i just feel sick. i feel like i'm just a black hole for all their hard work. if i could just... stop being the problem, maybe they could actually breathe again. does that sound crazy? like, is it really that much more logical to just remove the source of the stress?",
